FROM title t, cast_info ci, movie_keyword mk
WHERE t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.kind_id  =  4 AND t.production_year  =  2008 AND ci.person_id  <  1596027 AND ci.role_id  >  6
